Package com.isti.traceview.common

Interface Summary
IEvent This base interface represents event, i.e some occasion with time and duration which can be plotted on channel's graph.
 

Class Summary
AbstractEvent Abstract class implements IEvent interface, it contains all common behaviors of events.
Configuration This class holds configuration data.
DefaultEvent Concrete class for very simple default event
Station Defines the station information.
TimeInterval Class to represent interval of time
TraceViewChartPanel This code was copied from JFreeChart ChartPanel class.
UniqueList<E> List which can contain only unique elements
Wildcard this class realize unix command line wildcard syntax
 

Enum Summary
Configuration.ChannelSortType Enumeration for channel sort type.
Configuration.PanelCountUnit Enumeration for panel count units, we can define how many of this units we want to see on graph panel
TimeInterval.DateFormatType Enumeration for string time representation formats.
